manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

playstore_details.description:
Crypto.com DeFi Wallet is the best crypto wallet to store, earn and grow your crypto assets. It is a non-custodial DeFi wallet where you own your crypto and your private keys. 

You can safely store your crypto in a highly secure environment. It also allows you to send and receive up to 100 cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin(BTC), Ethereum(ETH), DeFi coins like Uniswap(UNI), Compound(COMP), yearn.finance(YFI), stablecoins and other ERC20 tokens. 

With the Crypto.com DeFi Wallet, it offers you a simple and secure way to access and explore DeFi projects. Deposit and earn the best returns on your DeFi tokens with DeFi Earn. Earn passive income without losing control with your crypto. Crypto.com DeFi Wallet is integrated with WalletConnect, allowing you to connect with DeFi Swap and other DApps by scanning the QR Code. Check out our app feature below! 

-Decentralized:
Gain full control of your crypto and private keys and manage up to 100 cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin(BTC), Ethereum(ETH), Litecoin(LTC), Lumen(XLM), XRP, CRO, Cosmos Network (ATOM), BAT, DeFi coins like Uniswap(UNI), Compound(COMP), yearn.finance(YFI), stablecoins like USD Coin(USDC), Tether(USDT), Dai and other ERC20 tokens.

-Convenient:
With the multi-wallets function, you can have more than one wallet under the Defi Wallet App by creating new wallets or importing existing wallets. Connect your Crypto.com DeFi Wallet to the Crypto.com App with your preferred wallet to easily access the diverse crypto financial services offered by Crypto.com. You can also connect with Crypto.com Defi Swap and other Defi projects with DeFi Wallet to farm your coins. 

-Secure:
Your private keys are encrypted locally on your device with Secure Enclave, protected by Biometric Authentication Technology and 2-Factor Authentication. Simplified backup and recovery with your unique 12-word backup phrase. 

-Flexible:
Send crypto at your preferred speed and network fee.

-Simple:
Helps you to navigate different crypto assets with a simple and user-friendly interface, supports up to 20 display fiat currencies. 

-Mainnet CRO Staking Rewards:
Mainnet CRO staking rewards are available on Crypto.com DeFi Wallet,  enabling one-click delegation of staking and rewards collection. It will be set at ~20%p.a. No minimum staking requirements.

-DeFi Earn with Compound:
Grow your crypto assets and earn passive income via DeFi Earn. DeFi Earn allow you to deposit your crypto assets to the Compound lending pool through native in-app integration. DeFi Earn gives you easy access to 12 DeFi tokens: Compound (COMP), ATOM, Yearn (YFI) BAT, DAI, ETH, UNI, USDC, USDT, WBTC, and ZRX — with more to come. There is no minimum term, and you can withdraw their deposit with the accrued interest at any time.

-DeFi Earn - Cosmos (ATOM) Staking:
Stake and earn ATOM tokens on DeFi Earn via the Bison Trail validator node. Earn an estimated return of 6 to 10% p.a. Restake your rewards to compound your interest.

-DeFi Earn - Yearn Earn V2:
Yearn Earn optimises the interest accrual process across multiple protocols to obtain the highest rates at all times. Deposits are automatically shifted between dYdX, AAVE, and Compound as rates change.

-Support DeFi Swap:
Swap ETH and many other ERC-20 tokens directly on the DeFi Wallet with DeFi Swap integration. It supports pairs in Ethereum (ETH), Crypto.com Coin (CRO), Uniswap (UNI), Dai (DAI), and many other ERC-20 tokens. 

-Integrated with WalletConnect: 
Explore DeFi Swap and other DeFi protocols by scanning the QR code with WalletConnect inside Crypto.com DeFi Wallet. 

-Ethereum Testnet Support:
Perform test transactions easily on the Testnet blockchain without the risk of losing your real funds. You can change your wallet network from Mainnet to Ethereum Testnets (Ropsten, Kovan, Rinkeby, and Goerli).

Customer Support: Got a question? Send us a message in the help centre. We will get back to you as soon as possible.
